text.tspan: Prevalence of schizophrenia in males vs. females, 2019
Share of male and female population suffering from schizophrenia. Figures attempt to provide a true
estimate (going beyond reported diagnosis) of schizophrenia prevalence based on medical,
epidemiological data, surveys and meta-regression modelling.
Data source: IHME, Global Burden of Disease (2019)
